  5) do while :- statements repeats until a specificed condition evaluates to false
      var i = 0;
      do {
      i += 1;
      console.log(i);
      }while(i < 5);
6) while:  while statements executes its statements as long as a specified condition evalutes to true.
         var n = 0;
         var x = 0;
         while(x < 3){
         n++;
         x += n;
         }


